title: The Townhall Weekend Journal for JUN-06-2014 FRI
description:
The Townhall Weekend Journal for JUN-06-2014 FRI



Obama's Bergdahl Blunder


Thursday, June 05, 2014


Obama's Bergdahl Blunder


Weekend Journal


Michael Medved with Colonel Ralph Peters on the Taliban's 
    Bergdahl release. 

Bill Bennett spoke with military historian Max Boot 
    about the Bergdahl situation. 

Michael Medved and Senator Marco Rubio discussed Obama's unilateral
    decision to release 5 Gitmo prisoners. 

Hugh Hewitt and CNN's Jake Tapper discuss Tapper's excellent
     reporting on Bergdahl's release. 

Bennett and James Pethokoukis 
    (blogger for the American Enterprise Institute) 
       discuss Obama's failure to lift the American economy.

Medved on Mayor Michael Bloomberg's excellent commencement address
 at Harvard where he calls-out the PC, 
    one-way thinking approach to teaching at our universities;
     and, as Bloomberg most pointedly accuses, at ivy league colleges.
 
Dennis Prager destroys Obama's lame attempt to push his climate change agenda.
